text: Länder (singular Land) or Bundesländer (singular Bundesland) is the name for (federal) states in 2 German-speaking countries. It may more specifically refer to: * States of Austria, the 9 federal subdivisions of Austria * States of Germany, the 16 federal subdivisions of Germany ==See also== * Land (disambiguation) Category:German words and phrases fr:Länder
title: Länder
